ygData.messageBody:
Thought I'd introduce myself...currently I'm a
tree elf (Beechwoodgrey)who hangs on the Lanys server
..right now i'm on level 6 and can't advance any
further.. i have a rusty sword so i'm stuck killing lesser
newbie prey till i can figure a way to get it sharpened
in Kelethin then maybe i can get back to killing
oc's and build myself up. If you have any suggestions
i'm listening :) otherwise i have to save up for a
new sword one bat wing at a time :(
